namedLocations.description: Arial, sometimes marketed as Arial MT, is a sans-serif typeface and computer font packaged with Microsoft Windows, other Microsoft software applications, Apple Mac OS X, and many PostScript computer printers. The typeface was designed in 1982 by Robin Nicholas and Patricia Saunders for Monotype Typography. Arial is also a typeface family comprising standard Arial (Arial Std) and variants, including Arial Black, Bold, Extra Bold, Condensed, Italic, Light, Medium, Monospaced, Narrow, and Rounded.
namedLocations.name: Arial

transcript.text: Hello everyone, we are happy to present new and enhanced custom Logo and art maker, a unique tool for your end clients to create custom logo and art instantly.
It makes it so easy for clients to create their custom logo and art and personalized wide range of products online.
So let us show you how it works.

You can enable custom logo and art maker in your own pin shop online storefront offering wide range of products like stationary, wide format, promotional, apparels, stickers, labels, invitations, photo products and lot more.
You can enable custom Logo and Art maker in your STML file designer studio so customer can use in wide range of products while they're personalizing in your online storefront.
Client can easily create their own custom logo and art in three simple steps.
First, they can choose the colour.
Second, they can add the custom tags such as their company names and tag lines.
It supports one line as well as multiple lines.
And now custom logo and art maker will present hundreds of options instantly and then client can choose the one they like.
After applying the art.
They can also further personalize each and every element like apply a different color or different fonts.
They can also save it and use it for any other product.
So they can create multiple logos and art in your website and use for the future ordering.
Also all the artwork and all the logos are also getting stored in their portfolio under their my account.
So they can edit it, create another version out of it.
They can also reuse it in the future.
In your on Pin Shop storefront back end, you can add unlimited clip arts and create layouts.
So custom Logo and Art maker will create hundreds of ready combinations for end customers while they are personalizing products in your online storefront.
So custom Logo and art maker will help you offer more personalized and value added services to your end clients.
If you want to know more, contact us at WWW dot on Pin shop.com and set up a personalized demo with our Web to Pin consultant.
